msgstr "Come funziona"

#: front-end/ad-platforms/views/page.php:296
msgid "Connect each platform once. Tokens are encrypted on this server and never leave it."
msgstr "Connetti ogni piattaforma una volta. I token sono criptati su questo server e non lo lasciano mai."

#: front-end/ad-platforms/views/page.php:297
msgid "On first connect, the last 3 years of daily spend are loaded in the background (90-day chunks every 30 seconds)."
